{"TopicId":169828,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Command pod moves?","CreatedByName":"tj.","CreatedById":184604,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-20T06:19:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"tj.","CreatedById":184604,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-20T06:19:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter successfully returning back to land, I noticed that you can move the mk1 command pod with the wasd controls as if it had small thrusters attached. This is curious since I do not see the monopropellent being reduced, only electricity and the only modules attached are the parachutes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-20T06:38:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223272885\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022169828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221516429194\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184604\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tj.\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, tj. said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter successfully returning back to land, I noticed that you can move the mk1 command pod with the wasd controls as if it had small thrusters attached. This is curious since I do not see the monopropellent being reduced, only electricity and the only modules attached are the parachutes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would be the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E system. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, so long as you have electricity, the hugely powerful reaction wheels in the pod can change your orientation, even on land.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tj.","CreatedById":184604,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-20T06:59:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223272890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022169828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221516430339\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would be the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E system. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, so long as you have electricity, the hugely powerful reaction wheels in the pod can change your orientation, even on land.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome! Thank you for the reply. That was really bothering me but now I understand.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-20T07:01:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223272898\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022169828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221516431553\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184604\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tj.\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, tj. said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome! Thank you for the reply. That was really bothering me but now I understand.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo problem! We all love to help new players here, so feel free to ask as many questions as your heart desires. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome aboard!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}